jalse.entities.annotations

Annotation Type EntityID


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
 @Repeatable(value=EntityIDs.class)
public @interface EntityID
    An Entity type annotation to represent a UUID.

    See UUID.UUID(long, long), UUID.fromString(String) and UUID.randomUUID().
    See Also:
    Functions.toIDSupplier(EntityID)
